title: Dave Matthews Band on VH1's Storytellers
description:
Dave and the guys drop by VH1&#039;s Storytellers and treat the audience to a well rounded portion of their well known hits! This telecast was capped and transcoded for your viewing pleasure with HD and WS viewing in mind. 

With the recent death of close friend and saxophonist LeRoi Moore , this episode will be remembered as a living tribute to the band as a whole and LeRoi as one of the members.

Songs in this episode include "You&#039;ll Figure it Out", "Ants March", "Too Much", "American Baby", and more.
